# natural_language_idea: Split 10 children into two labeled teams of 5 and 5.
# 中文题意: 将 10 个孩子分成两个有标号的 5 人队。
# 中文思路: 用有标号分组公式，验证 10!/(5!5!)=252。
# litex_code: this file
# proof_attempt: Model labeled teams abstractly and verify the arithmetic.
# status: blocked
